data.description: Check out Newton County's Freshest 4br 2ba on a unfinished basement -  2 acre lot with a He-Shed, She-Shed, and a Chicken Coup, and a separate Fenced in Dog Yard and 2 Aquaponics!!  Stainless Steel Upgrade Appliances, FARM House Sink and all through updated Bathrooms and Kitchen - This home loved by its sellers put all the right finishes and touches on this home to make it Move in ready including upgraded kitchen with bamboo flooring and butcher block counters with tile backsplash. The garden, chicken coup area and matured trees include Pear, Peach, Apple and Fig Trees. In the garden and yard, there are Strawberries, Raspberries and Blueberries and Grapes. All Appliances stay including the washer and Dryer and Antique Black Pantry Cabinet in the Dining room. Don't miss out on this perfectly updated, well kept and matured yard well landscaped for its next owner. Roof is just  3 years NEW!!
